Author: fefebear
Text: I missed that episode! I remember that one when Master Popo hyped up the magic bean and Goku just thought of all the food he can eat when he gets to the tower only to find magic beans.

Author: TheManyArchetypes
Text: Senzu beans were introduced in original Dragon Ball.  Yajirobe eats too many and turns into a sphere.  Don't binge eat sensu beans kids!
